<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.4">
<l>ēḻaipē taiyōrpā lakaṉvanteṉ peṇmaka ḷaiyeḷki</l>
<l>tōḻimārpa larkoṇṭu pōycceyta cūḻcciyai yārkkuraikkēṉ</l>
<l>āḻiyāṉeṉ ṉumāḻa mōḻaiyil pāycci yakappaṭutti</l>
<l>mūḻaiyup paṟiyā tateṉṉum mūturai yumilaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Many friends came, disparaging my daughter</l>
<l rend="indent">–a foolish, simple child–</l>
<l>to whom do I speak</l>
<l rend="indent">about [their] intention to lead [her] astray?</l>
<l>Having pushed [her] into the deep pool</l>
<l rend="indent">called “discus-bearer”</l>
<l>you have trapped [her].</l>
<l>She does not [know] the old saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“a ladle does not taste the salt”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
